      "content": "but i see it in their eyes. they're so much better when i'm not around to mess things up. sometimes i think the most loving thing i could actually do for them is to just... stop being a part of their lives. to just leave them to grow up without my shadow hanging over them. wouldn't that be more selfless than staying and making them suffer through my mistakes?",
